data.description: Charming 3 bedroom brick home located in Jacksonville with 2 car detached garage. 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom apartment located in upstairs garage for rental income, mother in law suite, or man cave! Home sits on a large, beautiful established lot with fenced in backyard.   Home boasts real hard woods, fireplace, fresh paint, new roof in 2019, updated dual pane windows, dehumidifier in crawlspace, and more!  Large kitchen with peninsula has a ton of cabinet space and updated fixtures.  Detached garage also had roof replaced in 2019. Has new vinyl flooring, paint, and mini-split AC/Heat. Garage has its own electric and water meters.So much charm in this home!
